  // Cleared shortcuts so Cmd+keys pass through (or at least aren't intercepted)
  // by cmux. Note: macOS terminals still don't forward Cmd to the TTY, so
  // emacs running inside a cmux terminal surface won't see these as super-mod
  // unless you switch to GUI Emacs (Emacs.app).
